'''格萊美博物館'''（{{lang-en|The Grammy Museum}}）是位於[[美國|美國]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的一座博物館，展示有關[[格萊美獎|格萊美獎]]和歷史和得獎者資料。格萊美博物館還設有一個可容納200人觀眾的劇場<ref name="Museum Minute">{{cite news |title=Museum in a Minute: Grammy Museum strikes a chord |first=Jon |last=Bream |author2=Ken Viste |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/travel/ci_12158930 |agency=[[Star_Tribune|Star Tribune]] |work=Star Tribune |publisher=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]] |location=San Jose Mercury News, 750 Ridder Park Drive, San Jose, CA 95190 |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |id=12158930 |date=April 16, 2009 |accessdate=April 29, 2009 |quote=The country's newest music shrine — the Grammy Museum, which opened in December — fits in downtown Los Angeles like another cowboy hat in Nashville. |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200913/http://www.mercurynews.com/travel/ci_12158930 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。博物館自開幕以來已舉辦超過300場公演。

